#284
Store Room~
To your surprise you able to get past the shopkeeper and into
her store room.  It appears that the store and this room were
originally all one room.  There are shelves that line walls 
holding the surplus inventory that is sold up front.  It appears 
that the store must be very busy because there is little dust on
anything.  You wonder how long you could stay back here before 
the shopkeeper would find you, you probably shouldn't wait
to find out!
